{
  "stem": "26983.9",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And all of us finished this postcard-- Apropos, we were only allowed to write 30 words, and only the first and second person, like I and-- and you, and that's that.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But we finished it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In German.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But we finished it in--",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It had to be in German.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It had to have be in German, as far as I remember.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "At least we wrote it in German.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And wrote, and with this, dear moti.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And moti means my death in Hebrew--",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--and this word every one of us knew-- I will finish.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we know now, because we asked our friends after the war, if they got these postcards, and they said yes.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they wondered, what does it mean, moti, that all of our boys wrote the same?",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But they couldn't imagine that it really means the deaths.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I also know about it that some people didn't care anymore and wrote explicitly that we are going to die in gas.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They will kill us in gas-- hoping that the censorship--",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, I used the word moti, my death.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And the same group of children I organized for this purpose.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But even these postcards came through.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But nobody could imagine that the people will be killed in gas.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "By the way, even in Auschwitz elderly people, mainly, didn't believe it.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I mean, at least from our transport.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Said no, they are transport at night, and the people who are going on selections.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And only you children have this, or the other people, have this imagination that they go through the chimney they are killed.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So even people who were in Auschwitz didn't believe that they will be-- that there is gas going on, just next around the corner.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not all, but many didn't believe.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
